    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Light two-wheeled hooded vehicles having springs and two shafts, drawn by one or more men. First used in Japan ca. 1870, but now common in other parts of the world.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
